oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Fisk University Choir program - 1946-11-25
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WSM broadcast of the Fisk University Choir, directed by John F. Ohl with organist Arthur R. Croley, and soprano soloist Lenora Lafayette. Recorded on the Fisk University campus.
